Man you=E2=80=99re never gonna read a better merger press release than this=
:Amalgamated Bank Announces Agreement to Acquire Amalgamated Bank of Chicag=
oNEW YORK AND CHICAGO =E2=80=93 September 22, 2021 =E2=80=93 Amalgamated Fi=
nancial Corp. (Nasdaq: AMAL), the holding company for Amalgamated Bank (=E2=
=80=9CAMAL=E2=80=9D), America=E2=80=99s socially responsible bank, today an=
nounced it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Amalgamated I=
nvestments Company, the holding company for Amalgamated Bank of Chicago (=
=E2=80=9CABOC=E2=80=9D), for approximately $98.1 million, which includes an=
 earnout of up to $1.1 million, in an all-cash transaction. Although the tw=
o entities have Amalgamated in the name, AMAL and ABOC are not currently af=
filiated.Aren=E2=80=99t banks great? Arguably the greatest bank name is Fif=
th Third Bank, which is what happened when the Third National Bank and Fift=
h National Bank merged. But if these guys go with Amalgamated Amalgamated B=
ank they will win. Very Amalgamated Bank. Twice-Amalgamated Bank. Amalgamat=
ed & Amalgamated Inc.=C2=A0The Amalgamation of Amalgamated Banks. My lord. =
Imagine being the investment banker who pitched this deal. =E2=80=9CWe thin=
k you should buy Amalgamated.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CWe are Amalgamated.=E2=80=
=9D =E2=80=9CNo I know hear me out.=E2=80=9D Imagine the first call between=
 the chief executive officers. =E2=80=9CHello Robert, this is Priscilla, I=
=E2=80=99m the CEO of Amalgamated Bank, I was hoping=E2=80=94=E2=80=9D=C2=
=A0=E2=80=9CWait wait wait wait just a minute,=C2=A0I=E2=80=99m=C2=A0the CE=
O of Amalgamated Bank.=E2=80=9D Anyway this is perfect, all mergers can sto=
p now, they have done the best one.One absolutely bizarre fact about the Am=
algamated Bank/Amalgamated Bank merger is that neither Amalgamated Bank nor=
 Amalgamated Bank appears to be amalgamated. The press release says:ABOC ha=
