<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">How strong is the force of capitalism?</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Max Abelson went t=
o <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25113962.260045/=
aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDktMjIvd2FsbC1=
zdHJlZXQtZGVhbG1ha2VyLXRyaWVzLXRvLXJlc3RhcnQtaGlzLXdlZWtuaWdodC1wYXJ0eS1zY2=
VuZQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB845605e9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D=
"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> a party at the Waverly Inn</a>:</p><blockquo=
te><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s sort of inspirational=
 how crowded it is,=E2=80=9D said Anthony Gellert, founder of Livingston Ca=
pital Management. =E2=80=9CI think the steak dinner matters,=E2=80=9D he ad=
ded. Then he made a prediction: =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s going to be an arms r=
ace again: Who=E2=80=99s going to offer golf and steak dinners more than th=
e other guy?=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Frazer Rice, who =
helps money managers for wealthy families at Pendleton Square Trust Co., pr=
edicted Wall Street parties will roar back, only to decline. =E2=80=9CYou h=
ave pent-up demand, let=E2=80=99s call it, for social interaction and busin=
ess interaction,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=80=9CThere will be an initial bump, =
and then the concepts of inequality and ESG are going to really take hold.=
=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Nearby, technology investor Sunda=
r Subramaniam disagreed. =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m not sure if the concerns of i=
nequality will withstand the pressure to close deals,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=
=80=9CThe force of capitalism is so strong they=E2=80=99ll do whatever it t=
akes.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">How necessary a=
re steak dinners to mergers-and-acquisitions activity? I would observe that=
 people who work in M&amp;A mostly think steak dinners are more important f=
or M&amp;A than people who do not work in M&amp;A do. =E2=80=9CLet=E2=80=99=
s disrupt investment banks by building an online M&amp;A platform,=E2=80=9D=
 tech types will say, and then the investment bankers will say =E2=80=9Cbut=
 how can you have a steak dinner on an online platform?=E2=80=9D This obser=
vation doesn=E2=80=99t imply that one side or the other is right. Perhaps t=
he M&amp;A bankers are dinosaurs ripe for disruption, as proven by their ar=
chaic insistence on steak dinners. Perhaps the tech types are na=C3=AFfs wh=
o=C2=A0misunderstand=C2=A0the essentials of the M&amp;A business, as proven=
 by their disregard for steak dinners. Anyway steak dinners seem to be back=
.</p><table class=3D"header" width=3D"100%" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" =
cellpadding=3D"0">
<tr>
<td class=3D"body-header-container" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; mso=
-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">McKinsey for Kids</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do think that an important skill in =
finance and consulting is taking a lot of complicated detailed unstructured=
 information, using it to form a clear thesis, and then presenting that the=
sis in a compelling and understandable way to an audience that has=C2=A0<em=
>not=C2=A0</em>spent time considering the details. =E2=80=9CGo learn about =
a difficult topic and explain it to a smart child=E2=80=9D seems like the s=
ort of thing that you ought to be good at if you are good at being a consul=
tant. Anyway McKinsey &amp; Co. =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/25113962.260045/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9u=
ZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDktMjEvbWNraW5zZXktY291bnNlbG9yLXRvLWNlb3MtdHJpZXM=
tY291cnRpbmctYS1uZXctYXVkaWVuY2Uta2lkcw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB73d0d48c" =
itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; tex=
t-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-colo=
r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">has create=
